   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1895_AS_RBH_1_00044"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb190427" type="place">I. Wollzeile 15</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1895_AS_RBH_1_00045"/>Lieber Richard!</salute></opener><p>In der <rs ref="#pmb42262" type="org"><hi rend="latintype">Meier</hi>i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen Strohhuthandlung</rs> am <rs ref="#pmb8" type="place">Prater</rs>, glaub ich oder <rs ref="#pmb42024" type="place">Frei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ingerga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e</rs>. –</p><p>Ob ich hingehe, wei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s ich nicht. Hab’ auch keine Einladung. Heut bin ich jedenfalls
               im <rs ref="#pmb34" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Griensteidl</hi></rs>.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
